  <entry>
    <title>python3 线程 进程 异步io性能对比</title>
    <link href="http://yoursite.com/2017/06/13/%E6%80%A7%E8%83%BD%E5%AF%B9%E6%AF%94/"/>
    <id>http://yoursite.com/2017/06/13/性能对比/</id>
    <published>2017-06-13T04:51:03.000Z</published>
    <updated>2019-01-21T10:01:47.405Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>&emsp;&emsp;目前网络上主流爬虫一般在使用requests、多线程、多进程,却很少有人使用协程异步这种</p><p>速度快占用资源少的爬取方式,当然爬虫的关键往往并不在于爬取速度的快慢,每种方式也有它各</p><p>自的适用场景,这里我们仅对网络io密集型进行简要的性能对比。</p><h3 id="1-多线程爬虫"><a href="#1-多线程爬虫" class="headerlink" title="1.多线程爬虫"></a>1.多线程爬虫</h3><p>&emsp;&emsp;众所周知由于python中一个线程需要执行任务，必须获取GIL,但是，在I/O阻塞的时候，解</p><p>释器会释放GIL。所以GIL在io密集型任务里仍有优异的性能表现,这里我们均以请求 <a href="http://wangfan.me" target="_blank" rel="noopener">wangfan.me</a></p><p>1000次为例进行测试,代码如下:</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> requests</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> threading <span class="keyword">import</span> Thread</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> time</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">url = <span class="string">'http://wangfan.me'</span></span><br><span class="line">headers = &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">'User-Agent'</span>: <span class="string">'Mozilla/5.0 (iPhone; CPU iPhone OS 11_0 like Mac OS X) AppleWebKit/604.1.38 (KHTML, like Gecko) Version/11.0 Mobile/15A372 Safari/604.1'</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">request_url</span><span class="params">()</span>:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> _ <span class="keyword">in</span> range(<span class="number">2</span>):</span><br><span class="line">        r = requests.get(url, headers=headers)</span><br><span class="line">        print(r.status_code)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span>:</span></span><br><span class="line">    s = time.time()</span><br><span class="line">    threads = []</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> _ <span class="keyword">in</span> range(<span class="number">500</span>):</span><br><span class="line">        threads.append(Thread(target=request_url))</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> t <span class="keyword">in</span> threads:</span><br><span class="line">        t.start()</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> t <span class="keyword">in</span> threads:</span><br><span class="line">        t.join()</span><br><span class="line">    print(<span class="string">'执行总用时 &#123;&#125;秒'</span>.format(time.time() - s))</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> __name__ == <span class="string">'__main__'</span>:</span><br><span class="line">    main()</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>程序执行结果:<br><img src="http://i2.bvimg.com/675051/11fa89e1e8227588.png" alt="Markdown"></p><p><strong>用时约12.6s!</strong></p><h3 id="2-多进程爬虫"><a href="#2-多进程爬虫" class="headerlink" title="2.多进程爬虫"></a>2.多进程爬虫</h3><p>&emsp;&emsp;由于进程之间的通信有操作系统传递，导致通讯效率低，切换开销大。所以一般密集CPU</p><p>任务，需要充分使用多核CPU资源（服务器，大量的并行计算）的时候用多进程。在编写爬虫</p><p>时不建议单独使用多进程来编写,代码如下:</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> requests</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> multiprocessing <span class="keyword">import</span> Process</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> time</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">url = <span class="string">'http://wangfan.me'</span></span><br><span class="line">headers = &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">'User-Agent'</span>: <span class="string">'Mozilla/5.0 (iPhone; CPU iPhone OS 11_0 like Mac OS X) AppleWebKit/604.1.38 (KHTML, like Gecko) Version/11.0 Mobile/15A372 Safari/604.1'</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">request_url</span><span class="params">()</span>:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> _ <span class="keyword">in</span> range(<span class="number">2</span>):</span><br><span class="line">        r = requests.get(url, headers=headers)</span><br><span class="line">        print(r.status_code)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span>:</span></span><br><span class="line">    s = time.time()</span><br><span class="line">    threads = []</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> _ <span class="keyword">in</span> range(<span class="number">500</span>):</span><br><span class="line">        threads.append(Process(target=request_url))</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> t <span class="keyword">in</span> threads:</span><br><span class="line">        t.start()</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> t <span class="keyword">in</span> threads:</span><br><span class="line">        t.join()</span><br><span class="line">    print(<span class="string">'执行总用时 &#123;&#125;秒'</span>.format(time.time() - s))</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> __name__ == <span class="string">'__main__'</span>:</span><br><span class="line">    main()</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>程序执行结果:<br><img src="http://i2.bvimg.com/675051/0aea7f4de19cc5bd.png" alt="Markdown"></p><p><strong>用时约17.7s!</strong></p><h3 id="3-异步爬虫"><a href="#3-异步爬虫" class="headerlink" title="3.异步爬虫"></a>3.异步爬虫</h3><p>&emsp;&emsp;async 与 await， 这是在 Python3.5 中引入的新语法，用于增强 Python 协程方面的支持。</p><p>可以简单的认为是asyncio.coroutine与yield from的简化版。随着新语法到来的还有async with</p><p> EXPR as VAR这个异步上下文管理器（取代with (yield from EXPR) as VAR)与async for TARGET</p><p> in ITER(取代for TARGET in (yield from ITER))这个异步迭代器。不同于yield from，await只适用</p><p>于 CO_COROUTINE标记的原生协程，即，使用async def语法定义的对象。由于requests并不支</p><p>持异步请求,所以请求库我们选择使用aiohttp(pip install aiohttp),参考代码如下:</p> <figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> time</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> asyncio</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> aiohttp</span><br><span class="line">url = <span class="string">'http://wangfan.me'</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">async</span> <span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">_get_page</span><span class="params">()</span>:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">"""</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">    获取并返回网页内容</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">    """</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">async</span> <span class="keyword">with</span> aiohttp.request(<span class="string">'GET'</span>, url) <span class="keyword">as</span> session:</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">async</span> <span class="keyword">with</span> session <span class="keyword">as</span> s:</span><br><span class="line">            print(s.status)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> __name__ == <span class="string">'__main__'</span>:</span><br><span class="line">    s = time.time()</span><br><span class="line">    a = [_get_page() <span class="keyword">for</span> _ <span class="keyword">in</span> range(<span class="number">20</span>)]</span><br><span class="line">    loop = asyncio.get_event_loop()</span><br><span class="line">    loop.run_until_complete((asyncio.gather(*a)))</span><br><span class="line">    print(<span class="string">'执行总用时 &#123;&#125;'</span>.format(time.time() - s))</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p> 程序执行结果:<br><img src="http://i2.bvimg.com/675051/bac5d957d31bac32.png" alt="Markdown"></p><p> <strong>用时约7.7秒!</strong></p><h3 id="测试结果"><a href="#测试结果" class="headerlink" title="测试结果"></a>测试结果</h3><p> &emsp;&emsp;根据测试结果不难看出,关于io密集型任务,异步&gt;多线程&gt;多进程,由于请求时可能受网络状况的</p><p> 影响,所以运行时间的结果,是经过多次运行选取了较为合理的中位值,这里异步爬虫仅用时7.7秒,最快</p><p> 时能达到5秒左右是测试前完全没有想到的,甚至在得到结果时一度以为aiohttp有缓存功能,但是当我</p><p> 将url更改为某网站翻页url,每次请求不同url时仍能保持该速度!!!多进程在执行时cpu完全跑满,导致本</p><p> 机操作卡顿,所以无论就速度而言还是占用资源来讲都不建议使用多进程来编写爬虫,线程任务选择了</p><p> 500线程每个线程请求两次速度上还是与异步有一定差距,所以如果要编写对爬取速度要求较高的代</p><p> 码时可以优先考虑aiohttp与asyncio的异步编程!</p>]]></content>
    
    <summary type="html">
    
      
      
        &lt;p&gt;&amp;emsp;&amp;emsp;目前网络上主流爬虫一般在使用requests、多线程、多进程,却很少有人使用协程异步这种&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;速度快占用资源少的爬取方式,当然爬虫的关键往往并不在于爬取速度的快慢,每种方式也有它各&lt;/p&gt;
